channel.description: Hey guys im having this issue when trying to connect to my server im running. I have the port 25565 opened and thats the port the server is running on. I compiled then ran the server, Im able to run it but not connect on my 718 client. *I *** My ip so people cannot get my ipadress.* Server settings - http://gyazo.com/933118c575fb3ed63c6f071e7f2d08f4 Client settings - http://gyazo.com/e83a3af4f26575da7894ef3863ab956d Now when I try to connect I get this issue. - gyazo.com/ae1662b7d1c955f05a231ea255c064b7 (Says error_game_js5connect) Right now any help would be appreciate. I've been trying to fix this and I just cannot.
